{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require the DVLA to provide detailed reasons for decisions and accept appeals",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "If you apply to change a vehicle classification and believe you meet all their written criteria the DVLA do not always agree, but there is no appeals process and they do not provide adequate information on why they have made their decision. We believe we should have the right to appeal",
